title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: A schedule change at home or work dramatically alters how you function at either place. An adjustment to a coworkers or household members routine could wreak minor havoc on normally smooth operations. Nevertheless, stay alert before pressing the panic button. Chances are this unplanned deviation surfaces a problem that was dormant until now. Suddenly, you can see how inefficient it is for someone to manage as many tasks as they do. Fortunately, this unexpected development puts you in a position to create a more egalitarian solution without anyone feeling frenetic. A positive attitude leads to a positive outcome.
